	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001048_0001"/><!--pb/@n='59r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hadley Green</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">27<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> June</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>You had better 
<lb/>keep the medal till 
<lb/>I come up myself<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>We made a call on 
<lb/>an old Mauritius 
<lb/>family in <placeName>Oxford 
<lb/>Square</placeName> on our 
<lb/>way and they 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001048_0002"/><!--pb/@n='59v'--> 
<lb/>gave us some 
<lb/>luncheon so the 
<lb/>time passed over 
<lb/>in which we 
<lb/>could have found 
<lb/>you &amp; did not 
<lb/>call, to say we 
<lb/>had met a first 
<lb/>cousin of your<reg>'</reg>s 
<lb/>in <placeName>New <choice><reg>C</reg><orig>c</orig></choice>ollege</placeName>
<lb/>who was very 
<lb/>civil to us, especially 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001048_0003"/><!--pb/@n='60r'--> 
<lb/>to <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L.</persName> with whom 
<lb/>he sat at dinner. 
<lb/><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hey gave us a 
<lb/>good reception 
<lb/>in the theatre. I 
<lb/>had declined to 
<lb/>give a lecture 
<lb/>on Tuesday but 
<lb/>if I had known 
<lb/>I would have 
<lb/>done it <add place="above">even</add> at the 
<lb/>expense of a sore 
<lb/>throat<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001048_0004"/><!--pb/@n='60v'-->
<lb/><p>I shall bring <persName>Kane</persName>
<lb/>the first time 
<lb/>I come - that fellow 
<lb/><persName>Arrowsmith</persName> always does that. You may 
<lb/>remember I gave 
<lb/>him <hi rend="underline">all</hi> about 
<lb/>six weeks ago except 
<lb/>one point which 
<lb/>has not yet come 
<lb/>and it would only 
<lb/>be a correction of what 
<lb/>is already published 
<lb/>if I don<reg>'</reg>t garrotte him I won<reg>'</reg>t do what he deserves<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>D Livingstone</p><addSpan spanTo="#p.59r" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fol. 59r'--></addSpan>
<lb/><p>He promised me a proof a month ago 
<lb/>and another on Wednesday last<reg>.</reg></p><anchor xml:id="p.59r"/>
			
</div>
